Images: ["[1-1685672958.jpg](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1685672958.jpg)", "[1-1685673050.png](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1685673050.png)", "[1-1685673094.png](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1685673094.png)", "[1-1685673145.png](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1685673145.png)", "[1-1685673180.png](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1685673180.png)"]

Topics: ['乌克兰战争', '军事', '政治', '新闻']

Keywords: ['乌克兰战争', '军事', '政治', '新闻', '乌克兰', '俄罗斯', '欧洲']

